Hello Mark, 

Thank you for connecting Netwrix Technical Support! 

Could you please clarify: what you need for the Power BI report? Just information on collected events or some specific Enterprise Auditor analysis results? Is it possible to use SQL view for Power BI? If so, please check the following view:

SA_FSAC_ActivityEventsView

Thank you!

Best Regards,
Ilia Kudashev
Support Engineer EMEA

Thanks for suggesting SA_FSAC_ActivityEventsView, I shall take a look.
